<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="iddcea27de-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="iddcea27df-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1996—Subsec. (b)(4). <ref href="/us/pl/104/105">Pub. L. 104–105</ref> added par. (4).</p>
</note>
</notes>
